{"tid":143313,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《美女與野獸》講基情 Kelly：同性戀都唔使㩒住","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T12:14:00.000Z","uid":22609,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6787356e093c667b555fe65841e4a7227fe563ae","tid":143313,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"《美女與野獸》講基情 Kelly：同性戀都唔使㩒住<br />\n<br />\n2017-03-04 16:46:36 HKT  <br />\n 有片：<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170304&amp;guid=56384379&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170304%26guid%3D56384379%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b8899feb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170304%26guid%3D56384379%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=69b95e79\" target=\"_blank\">hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170304&amp;guid=56384379&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼真人版電影《美女與野獸》（Beauty and The Beast） 將於下星期上映，雖然呢套電影喺香港列為一級，但係都惹嚟唔少家長爭議，因為導演比爾干頓（Bill Condon）更改原著劇情，將飾演加斯頓嘅盧克伊雲斯（Luke Evans）與手下來富（Josh Gad飾）嘅主僕關係，變成同性戀情節。<br />\n<br />\n結果有保守派家長要求迪士尼只製作合家歡電影，甚至有海外同香港家長團體不滿，發起聯署反對同性戀平權內容，又喺facebook開po要求聯署抗議迪士尼向兒童宣傳同性戀信息，跟住又貼出兩個聯署反對迪士尼喺電影宣傳同志觀念嘅美國網站，呼籲網民踴躍簽署。(新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lGmW6W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lGmW6W&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=84fd6786\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lGmW6W</a> )<br />\n<br />\n今日陳慧琳(Kelly)喺銅鑼灣出席二手衫慈善義賣優先場活動，本身係二子之母嘅Kelly，講到《美女與野獸》加插同性戀情節，Kelly話：「我會自己睇咗先、過濾咗先。我嗰啲太細唔知咩事，大啲知道就要解釋畀佢哋聽，人係有呢個取向，我唔會抗拒話畀小朋友聽，o依家好open，最重要係自己知道自己要啲乜嘢，就算係同性戀都唔使㩒住『我係鍾意異性』，我覺得唔需要，等佢早啲知道『乜原來唔係一個罪』，唔好覺得自己做錯事，灌輸正確態度畀佢哋知，我會咁樣教。」<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488614369_e133.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170304%2Flarge%2F1488614369_e133.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=db8216d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488614369_e133.jpg[/img]</a><br />\nKelly喺銅鑼灣出席二手衫慈善義賣。(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488614371_47c5.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170304%2Flarge%2F1488614371_47c5.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7d214822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488614371_47c5.jpg[/img]</a><br />\nKelly話自今次有過百對鞋、過千件衫，仲有手袋、飾物義賣。(攝影：陳俊強)(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488614377_e388.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170304%2Flarge%2F1488614377_e388.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b55b9567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488614377_e388.jpg[/img]</a><br />\nKelly又拎住一條色彩繽紛嘅長裙話：「喺法國拍廣告時買，我好似冇著過，色彩好繽紛，可以掛喺度欣賞。」(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\nKelly拎住個仔嘅外套不停咁「嗦」。<br />\n<br />\n今次Kelly今次自己落手落腳set場。"},{"pid":"5a6cba143dd0e118b945a04511607543c2c49666","tid":143313,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/215657_0e5fa7186518192c21a18e3c2b13f4ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F215657_0e5fa7186518192c21a18e3c2b13f4ba.jpg&h=8862da9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6G9T57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6G9T57.jpg&h=012bc518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d40a1f74ea5fcc24ec2ecf46f3e4eaab10f4c08","tid":143313,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b63d0c75c08df4edee347dd6b2995be614e3fbf0","tid":143313,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4609c039622206bdbcaa027a8837852ae8ed1c3f","tid":143313,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講就咁講</blockquote><br />\n答乜都唔啱聽架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daabc8915b0017475714cf140e8be62fdaeb657","tid":143313,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講就咁講</blockquote><br />\n答乜都唔啱聽架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明細細個比佢知有同性戀有咩問題？<br />\n等佢愈大，接受力愈低先比佢知？on9"},{"pid":"02f023865ffd32354c5783989e8153ae537612c8","tid":143313,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:45:13.000Z","msg":"fb睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n//美女與野獸 人獸交<br />\n白雪公主迷戀屍體<br />\n花木蘭 易服癖+非禮<br />\n青蛙王子 人獸+虐畜<br />\n風中奇緣 跨種族雜交<br />\n人魚公主 貪圖男色<br />\n長髮姑娘 玩囚禁<br />\n灰姑娘 戀鞋癖<br />\n阿拉丁 玩偷情<br />\n家長們 做嘢啦！//"},{"pid":"f6e877de5af4abea75af7a476ed57c08cefbdd89","tid":143313,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講就咁講</blockquote><br />\n性取向呢D可以講道理講到由攣變直?"},{"pid":"b7060dd2affaf4cd2e565c08d6b2ed1eca73780a","tid":143313,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}